@page "/support"
@layout MainLayout

<PageTitle>Support | SPC Technology</PageTitle>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <p class="eyebrow">Support</p>
            <h1>Support</h1>
            <p class="lead">
                SPC Technology provides operational support for organizations using Phoebus ERP in their daily business processes.
            </p>
            <p>
                If you require assistance with system usage, operational issues, or technical questions, you can use the support channels below to reach the appropriate support team.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Submit a Support Ticket</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    For most support requests, the recommended method is to submit a ticket through the Phoebus support portal.
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>
                The ticket system allows our support team to track issues, provide structured responses, and maintain clear communication throughout the resolution process.
            </p>
            <div class="actions">
                <a class="button button--primary" href="https://phoebus.asia/Tickets/New" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Submit a Ticket</a>
            </div>
            <p>Typical support requests include:</p>
            <ul class="bullet-list">
                <li>Product usage questions</li>
                <li>Operational or workflow issues</li>
                <li>System error investigation</li>
                <li>Configuration guidance</li>
                <li>Follow-up requests related to previous support cases</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Operational Support</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    Our support team assists customers with the day-to-day operation of Phoebus ERP.
                </p>
            </div>
            <ul class="bullet-list">
                <li>Guidance on business workflows within the system</li>
                <li>Assistance with financial and operational processes</li>
                <li>Clarification of system behavior or configuration</li>
                <li>Help resolving operational interruptions</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Support is provided with the goal of helping organizations maintain smooth and reliable ERP operations.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Customer Documentation and Guidance</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    SPC Technology continues to expand customer guidance and documentation for Phoebus ERP.
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>As these resources are organized, customers will be able to access:</p>
            <ul class="bullet-list">
                <li>Operational guidance</li>
                <li>Product usage explanations</li>
                <li>Configuration references</li>
                <li>Best practices for system operation</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Documentation resources will be made available through the support portal and customer communication channels.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-shell">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Direct Support Contact</h2>
                <p class="section-intro">
                    If you require direct assistance, you may also contact the support team.
                </p>
            </div>
            <ul class="bullet-list">
                <li>Helpdesk portal: <a href="http://phoebus.asia/Tickets/New" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://phoebus.asia/Tickets/New</a></li>
                <li>Support phone: +84 287 037 6896 - Ext 183</li>
                <li>Consultant: +84 287 037 6896 - Ext 184</li>
                <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@spc-technology.vn">support@spc-technology.vn</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
